multinational force "to take all necessary measures" to restore
peace and ensure that the territory moves toward independence.
</P>
<P>
Clinton has announced to send hundreds of troops to
participate in the multinational force in East Timor, but has
decided to exclude the troops from potential combat situations.
</P>
<P>
The hundreds of American troops would perform logistical,
intelligence and communications duties, keeping clear of any
outbreaks during U.N. peacekeeping operations. 
