Fair opened today in the capital of China's Ningxia Hui Autonomous
Region.
</P>
<P>
It is sponsored by the autonomous regional government as one of
the major events for promoting the opening up and development of
the area.
</P>
<P>
Nearly 300 enterprises from across the country and 19 cities
have sent delegations to the fair.
</P>
