paintings exhibition, a pottery show, a display of relics, a
fashion show, and ethnic group performances.
</P>
<P>
Ningxia has improved its investment environment in recent years
and it now has 400 overseas-funded enterprises with an aggregate
investment of 400 million U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
It has also had 3,300 different exchanges and cooperation
projects with eastern and western parts of the country which
invested a total of 700 million yuan in the region and thus helped
increase the region's output value by 2.3 billion yuan.
