<HEADLINE> Palestinian Team for Transition Negotiation Control </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GAZA, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Palestinian National Authority
Chairman Yasser Arafat endorsed Wednesday evening the list of
Palestinian team in the Supreme Steering and Transition
Negotiations Control Committee.
</P>
<P>
