Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Then a date will be fixed in the near future for a meeting of
the supreme steering and control committee to supervise the
implementation of all matters related to the transition period.
</P>
<P>
Erekat said that the Palestinian side had communicated with the
Israeli side at a meeting held Wednesday over the formation of the
Palestinian team in the committee and relevant subcommittees. The
team, he said, is separate from the Palestinian delegation for the
final status talks.
</P>
<P>
At the meeting, the Palestinian side also delivered a number of
records and lists of the Palestinian police force in line with the
recent Sharm el-Sheikh Memorandum.
</P>
<P>
Erekat said he will lead the Palestinian team in Supreme
Steering and Transition Negotiations Committee, which also
includes ministers of civil affairs, economy and justice, as well
as Colonel Mohamed Dahlan, chief of the Palestinian preventive
security department. 
</P>
</TEXT>
