railway crossing located somewhere between Surodadi station and
Pemalang as the express train had just reached the same point at
high speed.
</P>
<P>
Immediately after the impact, the bus got hooked to the train
which dragged the bus along over a distance of about 500 meters.
</P>
<P>
Widowo did not say how many people had been traveling in the
bus and whether any of the train passengers had been wounded.
</P>
<P>
He only said at least six other people from the bus were rushed
to hospital for emergency treatment due to their serious injuries.
 
