trying for the restoration of peace there." But the cooperation of
other countries is essential for that, he added.
</P>
<P>
"There are our six neighboring countries plus Russia and
America. This issue will also come under discussion," he said.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, Aziz said, there is the Indian nuclear doctrine,
which is dragging Pakistan towards a nuclear arms race. "We shall
highlight the fact that in the present circumstances Indian
nuclear doctrine is not suitable."
</P>
<P>
"We want the world to persuade India to prepare nuclear policy
through mutual consultation. We have already suggested the Nuclear
Free State Regime to India. This is the third issue which will be
discussed there," he said. 
