statistics said, adding that the mileage has extended to 6,058.4
km in 1999 from 4,468 km in 1988.
</P>
<P>
It is also reported that 257.6 km more of railroads are under
construction and another 832 km of such roads are projected to be
built.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, during the 11-year period, 114 bridges including 12
major ones have also been built, the statistics added. 
