agencies, the People's Liberation Army, the governments of every
province, autonomous region, and municipality, and the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (SAR) Government.
</P>
<P>
"Leaders of the central government have attached great
importance to this exhibition. President Jiang Zemin personally
inscribed the name for it," Wang told the conference here.
</P>
