<HEADLINE> Chinese President Back from Asia-Pacific Tour </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 16 (Xinhua)-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
returned to Beijing late today by special plane after winding up a
state visit of Thailand, Australia and New Zealand, and attending
the 7th APEC Informal Leadership Meeting.
</P>
<P>
Premier Zhu Rongji, Vice-President Hu Jintao, Vice-Chairman of
the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress Tian
Jiyun, Vice-Chairman of the Central Military Commission Zhang
Wannian, and other senior officials as well as diplomatic envoys
