Hall of the People.
</P>
<P>
Also back by the same plane were Jiang's wife Wang Yeping, Vice
Premier Qian Qichen and his wife Zhou Hanqiong, Director of the
General Office of the CPC Central Committee Wang Gang, and
Minister in charge of the State Development Planning Commission
Zeng Peiyan, among other senior officials.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
