point to 185.26, the Industrial Index slipped 9.04 points to
1,262.95 while the Second Board Index inched up 0.05 of a point to
158.18.
</P>
<P>
Gainers outnumbered losers by 367 to 213 while 133 counters
were unchanged and 205 untraded.
</P>
<P>
The day's total turnover slightly declined to 148.836 million
shares valued at 403.744 million ringgit (106.248 million U.S.
dollars) from Wednesday's 149.35 million shares worth 465.52
million ringgit (122.505 million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
