dollars, Commonwealth dropped 20.7 cents to 23.10 Australian
dollars, Westpac gave up 18 cents to 9.17 Australian dollars and
ANZ slid 12 cents to 10.08 Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 461.42 million shares traded for 1.39
billion Australian dollars (917 million U.S. dollars). Falling
stocks outnumbered rising stocks by 772 to 490, while 538 stocks
closed steady. 
