<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 16 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on
the Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,645.51 points today,
down 17.29 points from the previous session, according to the
Guangfa Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSE-30 index, based on 30 blue chips selected from more
than 400 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai Stock
Exchange, closed at 3,727.94 points, down 32.02 points from the
previous session.
</P>
<P>
A Share Index: 1,748.56 points, down 18.33 points;
</P>
<P>
