<TEXT>
<P>
The 6,700-ton Admiral Panteleyev from Russia's Pacific fleet
arrived Thursday morning in Yokosuka, where the headquarters of
Japan's Maritime Self-defense Force (MSDF) fleet is located, the
reports said.
